Distance

  • What is a point?
  • What is the distance between two samples?

A point: \( (Y_{i,1},\dots,Y_{i,8793})' \)

Distance between two points:

\[ d(h,i) = \sqrt{ \sum_{j=1}^{N} (Y_{h,j}-Y_{i,j})^2 } \]
